      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AUSSIE STRIKE (1) finished sixth last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 390m at Ballarat, taking a Mix 6/7 H in an enormous 21.86. Has the ability and expected to go close again. SPRING QUIZ (8) missed the frame last time when fourth (24.77) at Bendigo but prior to that had two placings in a row. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. A big run wouldn't surprise. GOLD STRIPES (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when eighth at this track over 390m behind Ridiculous (22.68) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Bold showing expected. NINETEEN CRIMES (7) is always hard to beat when drawn in this box.",
